<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">الجذر:</span>هـ د ر<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">مثال:</span>أَصْبَح مَهْدور الدم<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">الرأي:</span>مرفوضة<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">السبب:</span>لمجيء اسم المفعول من الفعل الثلاثي المجرد <span class="c2">«هَدَرَ»</span>.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
